---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations } from '../i18n/utils';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<head>
  <title>Manifesto per la Giustizia — BoycottWithAI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Strategie multi-dimensionali di pressione: boicottaggi, attivismo digitale e azioni non-violente. Guida pratica per organizzatori." />
</head>

<Base>
  <section>
  <h1>{t('manifesto.title')}</h1>
  <p class="muted">{t('manifesto.subtitle')}</p>
  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('manifesto.vision.title')}</h3>
    <p class="muted">{t('manifesto.vision.p1')}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('issues.title')}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>{t('issues.core')}</li>
      <li>{t('issues.escalation')}</li>
      <li>{t('issues.humanitarian')}</li>
      <li>{t('issues.institutions')}</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('issues.core')}</h3>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.core.evidence')}</p>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.core.relevance')}</p>
    <p><strong>Action:</strong> {t('issues.core.action')}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('issues.escalation')}</h3>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.escalation.evidence')}</p>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.escalation.relevance')}</p>
    <p><strong>Action:</strong> {t('issues.escalation.action')}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('issues.humanitarian')}</h3>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.humanitarian.evidence')}</p>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.humanitarian.relevance')}</p>
    <p><strong>Action:</strong> {t('issues.humanitarian.action')}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
    <h3>{t('issues.institutions')}</h3>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.institutions.evidence')}</p>
    <p class="muted">{t('issues.institutions.relevance')}</p>
    <p><strong>Action:</strong> {t('issues.institutions.action')}</p>
  </div>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:18px">
      <h2>{t('manifesto.methods.title')}</h2>
      <ul>
        {t('manifesto.methods.list').map(item => (
          <li>{item}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </article>

      <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
        <h2>{t('manifesto.antiwar.title')}</h2>
        <p>{t('manifesto.antiwar.p1')}</p>
        <ul>
          <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.policies') || 'Policy advocacy for disarmament and arms-export bans'}</li>
          <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.divest') || 'Divestment campaigns targeting defense contractors'}</li>
          <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.education') || 'Public education on the costs of militarization and peaceful alternatives'}</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
      <h2>{t('manifesto.antiwar.title')}</h2>
      <p>{t('manifesto.antiwar.p1')}</p>
      <ul>
        <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.policies') || 'Policy advocacy for disarmament and arms-export bans'}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.divest') || 'Divestment campaigns targeting defense contractors'}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.antiwar.education') || 'Public education on the costs of militarization and peaceful alternatives'}</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
      <h2>{t('manifesto.values.title')}</h2>
      <p>Regola del 3,5%: la ricerca mostra che raggiungere ~3.5% della popolazione attiva può rendere inevitabile il cambiamento politico. Focus su:</p>
      <ul>
        {t('manifesto.values.list').map(item => (
          <li>{item}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
      <h2>{t('manifesto.failures.title')}</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>{t('manifesto.failures.environment')}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.failures.energy')}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.failures.investment')}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.failures.health')}</li>
        <li>{t('manifesto.failures.ai')}</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
      <h2>{t('manifesto.methods.title')}</h2>
      <p>{t('manifesto.methods.list')[0]}</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card" style="margin-top:12px">
      <h2>Escalation e Sostenibilità</h2>
      <p>Seguire una progressione per fasi aiuta a mantenere controllo e legittimità. Fasi raccomandate:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Sensibilizzazione e costruzione di coalizioni (settimane 1-4)</li>
        <li>Azioni dimostrative e mobilitazione (settimane 4-12)</li>
        <li>Disobbedienza civile e pressione economica mirata (settimane 12-24)</li>
        <li>Sostenimento e istituzioni alternative (oltre 24 settimane)</li>
      </ol>
  <p>Mantenere non-violenza, rotazione di responsabilità e supporti contro il burnout.</p>
  <p class="muted" style="margin-top:12px">{t('manifesto.callToAction')}</p>
      <h3>Prompt rapido per organizzatori</h3>
      <p class="muted">Usa questo schema per iniziare: identificare l'obiettivo, mappare punti di leva, stabilire metriche di successo, pianificare fasi, assegnare ruoli, testare una piccola azione pilota.</p>
    </article>

  </section>
  <section style="margin-top:20px">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>What you can do</h3>
      <p class="muted">{t('manifesto.callToAction')}</p>
      <div style="margin-top:10px">
        <a class="button" href={`/${lang}/get-involved/`}>{t('cta.join')}</a>
        <a class="secondary" href={`/${lang}/resources/`}>{t('resources.title')}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
